# 🎓 Nobel Internship Flyer

A responsive and animated HTML flyer for promoting the Nobel Internship Program. This web flyer is designed to engage users with clean visuals, smooth animations, and a strong call-to-action.

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 Clean, modern layout
- 🖼️ Animated flyer and logo
- 🌍 Responsive design (mobile-friendly)
- 💡 CSS animations on hover
- 📌 Background image and Nobel logo support
- 🔗 Clickable "Register Now" button that links to Nobel's official internship page

